text:
I submitted nvi-m17n (multilingual nvi) related ports.
There was a mistake in pkg/PLIST in those files, so I would
like to send an update.

Fix: 

Please append the following lines, to pkg/PLIST in each of
the nvi-m17n directories:

@dirrm share/vi/catalog
@dirrm share/vi/perl
@dirrm share/vi/tcl
@dirrm share/vi
How-To-Repeat: none
